{"tid":603920,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"湯家驊：跟張曉明單獨公園賞櫻「很浪漫」","createTime":"2018-03-24T08:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-26T02:39:09.000Z","uid":20933,"like":88,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"802cc2a076e6d543636c6211327d28558c392150","tid":603920,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:07:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180324/s00001/65f2a1be9cfbcc71bc941705f3419418.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180324%2Fs00001%2F65f2a1be9cfbcc71bc941705f3419418.jpg&h=b3710957&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主思路正在北京訪問，召集人湯家驊透露，他昨日跟港澳辦主任張曉明單獨會面一個多小時，其間張曉明帶他到玉淵潭公園欣賞北京初開的櫻花，雙方談及很多港人關注的課題，包括23條立法、修憲及香港司法獨立等。<br />\n<br />\n他覺得這次會面「很特別、很浪漫和有戲劇性」。他表示，不會覆述張曉明其間所言。"},{"pid":"335c9d41b29a5ecfa5fb3b0ca7e8d859a8d7b09a","tid":603920,"uid":35014,"like":113,"dislike":0,"score":113,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:09:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f97e5202d55a54c99e6e619db567ef5de525d913","tid":603920,"uid":76115,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:09:50.000Z","msg":"雪廠街單獨賞嫩菊都好浪漫"},{"pid":"66d8df6b6f91600bf742d117bf4f3d19dc3c82b8","tid":603920,"uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:10:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180324/large/1521877169_561b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180324%2Flarge%2F1521877169_561b.jpg&h=2ceaea35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n民主思路訪京團今早到港澳辦，與港澳辦主任張曉明及副主任馮巍會面。召集人湯家驊會後指，自己和張曉明經過2小時單獨見面後，一起到附近的公園欣賞櫻花，形容是次會面是「特別、浪漫和戲劇性」。而全國人大常委譚耀宗早前指，日後立法會參選人如有「結束一黨專政」的口號，可能會違反憲法，但有消息人士引述張曉明稱，違憲之說並非「官方的講法」。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊提到，會面間與張曉明討論包括「內地修改憲法」、「23條立法」及「香港司法獨立」等議題，強調自己已「清楚表達港人觀點」，雖然對方表示明白，但湯稱目前不能引述對方的回覆。而對於譚耀宗疑似「假傳聖旨」，湯家驊認為雖然參選人理應尊重憲法，但根據香港的現行法例下，沒有任何理由要求參選人「擁護共產黨」。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊就「23條立法」都有分別與張曉明及馮巍對話，他指感受不到對方心中有23條立法的既定時間表，亦沒有特別要求特區政府在某個時段處理立法。湯又指，23條立法的問題不可能一次就解決，亦非個人能力可以處理，強調立法需經中央政府和社會各方討論和研究。"},{"pid":"108e5fe0d4eb622a443d33f705269c77d4b301f3","tid":603920,"uid":51129,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:11:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>G</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"2ab4845c37b596a3cb72b6676f30538035d6113f","tid":603920,"uid":62815,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:12:27.000Z","msg":"賞菊？"},{"pid":"86d19157fbc565bc067936c40c92ea744283f74e","tid":603920,"uid":47359,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:12:30.000Z","msg":"十一驊"},{"pid":"e049539af268042447ac30da66da158a336bc528","tid":603920,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:13:49.000Z","msg":"又唔屌得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁呀讚囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中間路線化干戈為玉帛，天下太平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b64f912ee4f48cdf5bf10da6600cc8c8d780b7","tid":603920,"uid":8048,"like":62,"dislike":0,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:14:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/finance/20120412/photo/0412-00204-002h1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20120412%2Fphoto%2F0412-00204-002h1.jpg&h=b8ac567a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4a62114e2bd156da5b7389343786acd150bd9ed","tid":603920,"uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:14:48.000Z","msg":"PTBF<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96c35af66cad2ba383fbd2eb35e20f86478a61a","tid":603920,"uid":57636,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-24T08:16:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/finance/20120412/photo/0412-00204-002h1.jpg\" data-thumb